{"tid":255012,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"朋友類型 最憎邊種入黎講下","createTime":"2017-05-23T15:01:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-23T16:09:42.000Z","uid":107294,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2f3f0fd9b0c98f53929848253e039003114a1529","tid":255012,"uid":107294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T15:01:35.000Z","msg":"依段經歷發生中二個時有個坐我格黎位既女同學<br />\n佢唔八婆 但最大問題無論嬲定開心笑同會勁大力打我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我真係頂唔順 佢仲要無自知之明<br />\n佢就爽啦 我就痛到仆街 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但問題你又唔可以話佢 因為佢會覺得佢唔係認真<br />\n我認真就小器 啪啪啪聲呀 救命 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n結果吊左位我就搵機會淡左段關係<br />\n無再做朋友 佢依家到畢業都無朋友 應該打走曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實係咁比佢打 真係好不爽 我又唔會還手 <br />\n一還手就真係格鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00ba4c51b21b45e44c0d73f0b9f6248b04314cc3","tid":255012,"uid":107294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T15:04:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依段經歷發生中二個時有個坐我格黎位既女同學<br />\n佢唔八婆 但最大問題無論嬲定開心笑同會勁大力打我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我真係頂唔順 佢仲要無自知之明<br />\n佢就爽啦 我就痛到仆街 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但問題你又唔可以話佢 因為佢會覺得佢唔係認真<br />\n我認真就小器 啪啪啪聲呀 救命 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n結果吊左位我就搵機會淡左段關係<br />\n無再做朋友 佢依家到畢業都無朋友 應該打走曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實係咁比佢打 真係好不爽 我又唔會還手 <br />\n一還手就真係格鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n另外都希望巴絲講解決依類朋友方法"},{"pid":"0076bfbed58019683052412d1ce762771042bdc2","tid":255012,"uid":7843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-